== 個人生活 ==
祖克曼與尤吉妮亞·里奇（Eugenia Rich）結縭於1968年<ref>{{Cite news|title=The Busy Life of Eugenia Zukerman, Flutist-Author|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1980/10/10/archives/the-busy-life-of-eugenia-zukerman-flutistauthor.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1980-10-10|accessdate=2022-04-10|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Raymond|last=Ericson|archive-date=2022-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220410052156/https://www.nytimes.com/1980/10/10/archives/the-busy-life-of-eugenia-zukerman-flutistauthor.html}}</ref>，兩人育有二女：歌劇歌者亞里安娜（Arianna Zukerman），以及藍調音樂、民謠音樂工作者娜塔莉亞（Natalia Zukerman）<ref>{{Cite news|title=WHAT THEY'RE DOING TOGETHER|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1979/03/11/archives/what-theyre-doing-together.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1979-03-11|accessdate=2022-04-10|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220410052156/https://www.nytimes.com/1979/03/11/archives/what-theyre-doing-together.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.westword.com/music/natalia-zukerman-5088535|title=Natalia Zukerman|author=Cole Haddon|work=West Word|date=2006-03-02|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620215853/https://www.westword.com/music/natalia-zukerman-5088535|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/11/fashion/weddings/11ZUKERMAN.html|title=Arianna Zukerman, Peter Sekulow|work=The New York Times|date=2007-11-11|page=921|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620220923/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/11/fashion/weddings/11ZUKERMAN.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。祖克曼於1985年離婚，他與演員{{tsl|en|Tuesday Weld|塔斯黛·韦尔德}}展開了第二段婚姻，這一段關係則持續至1998年為止。祖克曼現與第三任妻室{{tsl|en|Amanda Forsyth|阿曼達·佛塞}}定居於紐約，並經常在舞台上連袂演出。

== 軼事 ==
祖克曼的演奏用琴是1742年製的瓜奈里名琴「杜什今」（Dushkin）。

